# Cursor Project Rules — Kognitos v1→v2 Migration Utility

You are working on an **internal autonomous migration agent** that ports Kognitos v1 (Legacy) processes to v2 (Current) Automations from HAR file capture.

**The big picture:** HAR in → bundle → IR → SOP/test plan → human OAuth setup → autonomous agent builds v2 → report out.

Tech: Next.js 15 (App Router) + TypeScript (strict) + Tailwind on Vercel. XState v5 for the agent. OpenAI GPT-4o for the Process Analyzer (Phase 1). Anthropic Claude for SOP/test-plan generation (Phase 3). MCP + REST for Kognitos v2 control. Persistence in Vercel KV (prod) / better-sqlite3 (dev).

---

